--- !u!114 &1818705789
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 1818705787}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: ee1702f5dba03b04491fca892bc0f2a3, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  dialogueText: {fileID: 1818705790}
  dialogueLines:
  - Welcome to Tutorial mode!
  - In this game, you have the chance to play as defender to slice fruit, or attacker
    who throws bomb to defender.
  - Let's try the defender first.
  - You need to first find the NUS Logo to scan, then click "Scan Image" button top-right.
  - Now you have saved your position to spawn fruit. When you're ready, click "Spawn
    Fruit".
  - Make your sword hilt's marker visible in camera. Once you see a sword, start
    slicing!
  - When you slice a fruit, you earn points!
  - Remember to have your hand's marker visible in camera as well. Do you see a hand
    in screen?
  - Try your hand's special skill!
  - Nice job!
  - You may see special fruits with a shape sticked to them. Slice the fruit in the
    shape as indicated!
  - You will earn points with special splash. If you fail to slice in correct way,
    you will not earn points!
  - Wrong slice, try another one!
  - Nice job!
  - Remember to avoid bombs at all cost!
  - Now let's check what attacker has to do.
  - Approach the NUS Logo again, for attacker bombs will automatically spawn at where
    the logo is. Have your hand shown in camera, and approach where the bomb is.
  - Great, you've grabbed a bomb!
  - Now, aim at the marker's position, make a "release" move!
  - Do you see your bomb flying in the right direction?
  - Well done! You have completed the tutorial to learn about both roles! You can
    click the "Quit tutorial" button to return to main page now. Have fun!
--- !u!114 &1818705790
